PY3 Instabase is now up and running for testing! — Please give it a spin here: https://35.190.119.18

The login details are here: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1I_R9AX_7jaiLGooONPcVa92GcFLOJ2Lkc-yx9CWgeZE/edit#gid=0

It’s not connected to the production database, so you can create things from scratch, or use the Test Drive which should have all the test files for UAT and such

Thanks @Karthik S @Ashish and everyone for getting this setup!
Our goal is to have PY3 running for US Markets customers in the October release — so the more testing / UAT we do now — the better that process will be!
